pm2 list                 # Check running processes
pm2 logs school-backend  # View logs
pm2 restart school-backend
pm2 stop school-backend
pm2 delete all           # Delete all processes
pm2 flush                # Clear logs
pm2 kill                 # Stop PM2 daemon












Explanation:

/controllers → API ke request-response handle karte hain (HTTP logic).

/services → Business logic aur DB queries handle karte hain. Ye functions reusable hote hain, controller me sirf call karte hain.

/models → Mongoose schemas.

/routes → API routes define karte hain, controllers ko attach karte hain.

/utils → Generic helpers (e.g., nanoid generator, date helpers).

/middlewares → Auth, validation, error handling, etc.



